{"tid":454098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真係一世都記得呀】一歲女童旅遊返港後，感染大腸桿菌。","createTime":"2017-10-31T23:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T23:44:43.000Z","uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89bf4fc036072c771097054de1a1320142548632","tid":454098,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:12:52.000Z","msg":"曾在峇里飲鮮橙汁一歲童證實感染含產志賀毒素大腸桿菌<br />\n<br />\n2017-10-31 HKT 19:52<br />\n<br />\n一名一歲女童上星期在印尼峇里曾飲用鮮橙汁，其後證實感染含產志賀毒素大腸桿菌，衞生防護中心正調查。<br />\n<br />\n中心表示，女童過往健康良好，自上星期四起腹瀉，其後入住仁安醫院接受治療，現已出院，情況穩定。她的糞便樣本經化驗後，證實含產志賀毒素大腸桿菌。<br />\n<br />\n中心初步調查顯示，女童在本月22至25日期間曾到峇里，飲過鮮橙汁，並無飲用未經消毒的牛奶或進食生的食物，亦無接觸動物或到過農場。她的家居接觸者在外遊期間曾經腹瀉，返港求醫後已康復。<br />\n<br />\n中心提醒某些大腸桿菌病菌株、例如產志賀毒素大腸桿菌，可產生強烈毒素，甚至引致由食物傳播的嚴重疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362325-20171031.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362325-20171031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=XhJKvJGZCZrAMg57pUK6GEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=3c7cf37d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362325-20171031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=95d466d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362325-20171031.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1d2423adbe673ccee9f769dabfdc087042c53c3c","tid":454098,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:13:49.000Z","msg":"口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985de8be2a18266abc666db260de1bea7bedaa05","tid":454098,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:13:59.000Z","msg":"一歲記條撚咩<br />\n<br />\n咁細個唔應該飛外地"},{"pid":"cb56024d3d5f8ad53c68819fabb8f9afa235ca46","tid":454098,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70a71480d05d08c146a3f38b13447ceac47ed38e","tid":454098,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一歲記條撚咩<br />\n<br />\n咁細個唔應該飛外地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲老母會咁講：「我個女不知玩得幾開心。」"},{"pid":"3a38e3206468cb3831e614c94c2883b66198c6df","tid":454098,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:17:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea8aeee40c55e2c80314a4472cd9f3b0e09f4524","tid":454098,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:25:34.000Z","msg":"on9 十歲前都咪撚帶啦 香港啲細佬咁撚溫室"},{"pid":"e26cb42116bfd44d450ee34660be03985e07b7a8","tid":454098,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9 十歲前都咪撚帶啦 香港啲細佬咁撚溫室</blockquote><br />\n都唔關溫室事，係個仔女太細。隔一陣又話要食訓厠所，玩死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋佢地邊記得"}]}